This project includes certain CORAS symbol assets derived from or copied from
CORAS-The-Explorer:

https://github.com/stverdal/CORAS-The-Explorer

The vendored package sources in
tex/latex/corasdiagram/icons-src/
are normalized copies of SVG assets from:

src/js/components/molecules/Editor/svg/

The package preserves the upstream CORAS symbol concepts, renames the files to
package-native stems, and generates package-local PDF and black-and-white
variants from those vendored SVGs.

